    &lt;CommentText&gt;Thank you for taking the time to share your recent experience with us. I'm sorry that the service that you received was less than our acceptable standard. Please see below the response from our Chief Pharmacist Paul:  
_We are sorry for your poor experience in the pharmacy shop. We understand that as there was a wait for prescriptions at the time of your attendance that you advised that you would collect the prescription the following day. Unfortunately the pharmacist did not have the opportunity to check that the products on the prescription were available prior to you leaving the shop. Normal practice, when products are unavailable and require ordering, would be to obtain a contact number so that you would be informed when the prescription was ready to collect and we are sorry that this did not happen on this occasion._  
Should you wish to discuss this further please do not hesitate to contact me  
